<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="anti-discrimination-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h1>Fighting discrimination and making travel more open to all</h1>
        <p class="lead">We're committed to building a community where everyone belongs.</p>
        
        <h2>Project Lighthouse</h2>
        <p>Project Lighthouse is our initiative to uncover, measure, and overcome discrimination when people book on Wanderlust. We use data to understand where discrimination occurs and develop solutions to address it.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Learn more about Project Lighthouse →</a>

        <h2>Our ongoing work</h2>
        
        <h3>Strengthening our policies and procedures</h3>
        <p>We continuously update our policies to prevent discrimination and ensure fair treatment for all members of our community.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Read our Nondiscrimination Policy →</a>

        <h3>Sharing more information about economic empowerment opportunities available on Wanderlust</h3>
        <p>We're committed to creating economic opportunities for underrepresented communities through hosting and experiences on our platform.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Wanderlust Entrepreneurship Academy →</a>

        <h2>Our commitment to fighting discrimination</h2>
        <p>We publish regular reports on our progress in fighting discrimination and building inclusion. These reports detail our initiatives, findings, and future commitments.</p>
        <div class="report-links">
          <a href="#" class="report-link">
            <span class="report-year">2019</span>
            <span class="report-title">Work to Fight Discrimination Report</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="report-link">
            <span class="report-year">2022</span>
            <span class="report-title">Six-Year Update on Fighting Discrimination</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="report-link">
            <span class="report-year">2024</span>
            <span class="report-title">Project Lighthouse Update Report</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2>The Wanderlust Community Commitment</h2>
        <p>When you join the Wanderlust community, you commit to treating everyone with respect and without judgment or bias.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Read the Community Commitment →</a>

        <h2>How we're taking action</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Automated detection:</strong> Using technology to identify and block discriminatory messages and behavior</li>
          <li><strong>Account reviews:</strong> Reviewing accounts that may have engaged in discriminatory behavior</li>
          <li><strong>Policy enforcement:</strong> Taking action against users who violate our nondiscrimination policy</li>
          <li><strong>Education:</strong> Providing resources to help hosts and guests understand their responsibilities</li>
          <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Publishing regular reports on our progress and challenges</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="cta-section">
          <h2>Report discrimination</h2>
          <p>If you've experienced or witnessed discrimination on Wanderlust, we want to know. Your report helps us take action and improve our community.</p>
          <a href="/get-help-with-safety-issue" class="btn btn-primary">Report an issue</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Quick links</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="#">Nondiscrimination Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Community Commitment</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Project Lighthouse</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Accessibility</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Disability Support</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Need help?</h3>
          <p>If you have questions about our policies or need to report an issue, our team is here to help.</p>
          <a href="/helpcenter" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Visit Help Center</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
